The contributors to the CP method have been directly or indirectly involved in the design, development, deployment, and scaling of hundreds of applications from Startups to the Fortune 500 to the Tech Giants of Silicon Valley.


We are a group of engineers and product leaders that seek to pioneer and promote better ways of developing software by leveraging technology and automation to push the bounds of Agile Software Development.

We are advocating for organizations to adopt Continuous Previews as an Agile-supporting method to improve and expedite how they build and release software. 
